224
00:47:20,570 --> 00:47:24,614
Radiating this goodwill to all beings in all directions.

225
00:47:27,458 --> 00:47:30,963
May all beings be free of greed and selfishness.

226
00:47:37,492 --> 00:47:41,177
May all beings be free of anger and ill will.

227
00:47:48,487 --> 00:47:52,574
May all beings be free of fear and anxiety.

228
00:48:00,666 --> 00:48:04,512
May all beings be free of ignorance and delusion.

229
00:48:12,068 --> 00:48:18,617
May all beings be kind and gentle, sympathetic and benevolent.

230
00:48:28,612 --> 00:48:32,177
May all beings be forgiving and compassionate.

231
00:48:40,349 --> 00:48:41,990
May all beings be joyful,

232
00:48:42,157 --> 00:48:44,960
and rejoice in the success of others.

233
00:48:54,615 --> 00:48:57,719
May all beings be peace loving and calm.

234
00:49:04,670 --> 00:49:08,315
