237
00:49:36,311 --> 00:49:40,197
Sabe, sata, sukita, hantu, three times.

238
00:49:40,677 --> 00:49:43,601
Sadhu, which means well done, three times.

239
00:49:44,273 --> 00:50:08,661
Sabhe satta sukita hantu Sabhe satta sukita hantu Sabhe satta sukita hantu Sadhu sadhu sadhu

